{
  "id": "60ab302dada2a8001c28adae",
  "title": "逃げを責めるのは農耕民バイアス",
  "created": 1621831729,
  "updated": 1679924467,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "60ab302dada2a8001c28adae",
      "text": "逃げを責めるのは農耕民バイアス",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621831729,
      "updated": 1621831737
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab3069aff09e00009051a8",
      "text": ">昔、会社を辞めて[モンゴル]へ留学するとき、「それって[逃げ]じゃない？」と言われた。答えに詰まった。でもモンゴルで[遊牧民]の文化では「逃げ」は[恥]ではないことを知った。彼らは勝てるときは進み、やばい時は逃げる。明日勝つために。「逃げ」を責めるのは[農耕民バイアス]かも。守るべき土地があるから。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621831785,
      "updated": 1658207810
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab3039aff09e00009051a4",
      "text": "https://twitter.com/ippeishimamura/status/1396432927014088709?s=21",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621831737,
      "updated": 1621831739
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab303baff09e00009051a6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621831740,
      "updated": 1621831740
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab30acaff09e00009051a9",
      "text": "確かに「敵が攻めてきて苦しい時に、逃げずに最後まで留まって死ぬまで戦うことが良いことである」という思想は、人間より土地が大事な場合には為政者にとって都合の良いものだな。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621831853,
      "updated": 1621831957
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab30b0aff09e00009051aa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621831856,
      "updated": 1621831856
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab30b0aff09e00009051ab",
      "text": "[善の定義]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621831856,
      "updated": 1621831981
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab312daff09e00009051ac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621831982,
      "updated": 1621831982
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab303aaff09e00009051a5",
      "text": "[逃げ]を責めるのは[農耕]民バイアス",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621831739,
      "updated": 1621831761
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab304aaff09e00009051a7",
      "text": "[死ぬのが良い思考]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621831754,
      "updated": 1676304175
    },
    {
      "id": "63ea5f1faff09e00000b4a52",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676304159,
      "updated": 1676304159
    },
    {
      "id": "641d0861aff09e00007c1d59",
      "text": "関連",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679624289,
      "updated": 1679624297
    },
    {
      "id": "641d0868aff09e00007c1d5b",
      "text": "\t[困難から逃げると強くなれない]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679624297,
      "updated": 1679624297
    },
    {
      "id": "641d0869aff09e00007c1d5c",
      "text": "\t[無責任感]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679624298,
      "updated": 1679624308
    },
    {
      "id": "641d0868aff09e00007c1d5a",
      "text": "\t[残存者利益]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679624297,
      "updated": 1679624384
    },
    {
      "id": "641d08b4aff09e00007c1d5d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679624372,
      "updated": 1679624372
    },
    {
      "id": "64219ce6aff09e00007342b2",
      "text": "[逃げる]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679924456,
      "updated": 1679924461
    },
    {
      "id": "64219ce9aff09e00007342b3",
      "text": "\t[逃げ続けるSNS]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
